02.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1283.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Blazing Wand</span><hr size=1> I just can't seem to get Undertow to pop for me.  Has anyone MQ'd the blazing wand?  I have the other pieces but the thought of loosing all of the items collected up to the Power of Fire turn in scares the hell out of me. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uyenillenin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yenil Lenin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#333333>(7/23/02 4:08:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm25.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1283.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Blazing Wand</span><hr size=1> I've MQ'd burning embers for another mage so I don't see a problem with doing the blazing wand. <p>Yenil Lenin<br>
